{"meta":{"title":"Moroni 1","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1?lang=spa","contentType":"text/html","audio":[{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ/2017-11-2300-moroni-01-64k-spa.mp3?download=true","voice":{"name":"audio"}}],"pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"62f1984a739e8107faf92cd4bb6d5d51988d3e82","data-aid":"124247264","data-aid-version":"4","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1","itemscope":"","itemtype":"http://schema.org/Article","lang":"spa","data-orig-id":"4cc48df2ea969ff61326326dfb6e80ff8776abe7","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"Moroni 1","description":"Moroni escribe para el beneficio de los lamanitas — Se mata a todo nefita que no niegue al Cristo. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C."},"pageSocial":{"title":"Moroni 1","description":"Moroni escribe para el beneficio de los lamanitas — Se mata a todo nefita que no niegue al Cristo. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"626\"></span>\n<h1 data-aid=\"124247476\" id=\"title1\"><span class=\"dominant\">El Libro de Moroni</span></h1>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"124247477\" id=\"title_number1\">Capítulo 1</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"124247478\" id=\"study_summary1\">Moroni escribe para el beneficio de los lamanitas — Se mata a todo nefita que no niegue al Cristo. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124247479\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>Ahora bien, yo, <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>Moroni</a>, después de haber acabado de compendiar los anales del pueblo de Jared, había pensado no escribir más, pero no he perecido todavía; y no me doy a conocer a los lamanitas, no sea que me destruyan.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124247480\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>Porque he aquí, sus <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>guerras</a> entre ellos mismos son extremadamente furiosas; y por motivo de su odio, <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>matan</a> a todo nefita que no niegue al Cristo.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124247481\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>Y yo, Moroni, no <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>negaré</a> al Cristo; de modo que ando errante por donde puedo, para proteger mi propia vida.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124247482\" id=\"p4\"><span class=\"verse-number\">4 </span>Por consiguiente, escribo unas pocas cosas más, contrario a lo que había supuesto; porque había pensado no escribir más; pero escribo unas cuantas cosas más, que tal vez sean de valor a mis hermanos los lamanitas en algún día futuro, según la voluntad del Señor.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124247483\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/moroni-son-of-mormon?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Moroni hijo de Mormón</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note2a\" data-full-marker=\"2a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124247484\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/12.20-23?lang=spa#p20\">1 Ne. 12:20–23</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note2b\" data-full-marker=\"2b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124247485\" id=\"note2b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/45.14?lang=spa#p14\">Alma 45:14</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note3a\" data-full-marker=\"3a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124247486\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/matt/10.32-33?lang=spa#p32\">Mateo 10:32–33</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/29.5?lang=spa#p5\">3 Ne. 29:5</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","associated":{"title_number1":[{"sizes":"250px","alt":"Mormón se despide de lo que una vez fue una gran nación","aspectRatio":"1.4349775784753362","height":"223","width":"320","missingAsset":"false","assetId":"5220c52e82405490705ddef18e279cbffd7788ab","srcset":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/c7/af/c7afb59cb16f9cc80e257b3417a55ebdf502d894/mormon_bids_farewell.jpeg 60w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/41/69/4169a2658cc442a5a91cfe0f73ba6048692c5546/mormon_bids_farewell.jpeg 100w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/8e/c6/8ec67ede5eaf78bb3547b9b958e0300438a76ea0/mormon_bids_farewell.jpeg 200w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/65/b7/65b7df96c502fc9845119cae43b280c41b83476a/mormon_bids_farewell.jpeg 250w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/83/9a/839aabe2c77dad1cae1db189d831d98d09ea97fc/mormon_bids_farewell.jpeg 320w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/86/f0/86f046a40c95b0f6e13fa469c72348e174b9151a/mormon_bids_farewell.jpeg 500w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/dc/f1/dcf19085daf5bd4582f9bfee480ce995b16990e8/mormon_bids_farewell.jpeg 640w","imgId":"5220c52e82405490705ddef18e279cbffd7788ab","src":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/83/9a/839aabe2c77dad1cae1db189d831d98d09ea97fc/mormon_bids_farewell.jpeg","id":"aside1_img1","altSource":"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/media/image/mormon-bids-farewell-5220c52","attribs":{"data-alt-source":"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/media/image/mormon-bids-farewell-5220c52","id":"aside1_img1","src":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/83/9a/839aabe2c77dad1cae1db